title: Roast On the Coast - Norge
overview: Six Norwegian comedians have packed their bags and traveled to Cyprus for a week of sun, swimming - and roasting! Each night, a new comedian will take the hot seat to have their life torn apart by the other comedians before the best roaster of the night is crowned. On the final day of the stay, the week's best roaster and the winner of Roast on the Coast -Norway will be announced.
